1
00:00:00,500 --> 00:00:01,270
Ah, President!

2
00:00:01,300 --> 00:00:02,200
Regarding next month...

3
00:00:02,200 --> 00:00:03,740
...your birthday party.

4
00:00:04,000 --> 00:00:05,610
As per your instructions,

5
00:00:05,610 --> 00:00:07,540
I've revised the invitation design.
Here is the final version.

6
00:00:07,540 --> 00:00:08,240
Please take a look.

7
00:00:08,510 --> 00:00:10,340
Also, after the birthday party,

8
00:00:10,380 --> 00:00:11,410
the company's public profile

9
00:00:11,410 --> 00:00:12,410
is projected to increase,

10
00:00:12,780 --> 00:00:13,680
as shown in this report.

11
00:00:13,680 --> 00:00:14,680
Hold on.

12
00:00:15,480 --> 00:00:16,280
Right here.

13
00:00:16,280 --> 00:00:17,780
This is a glaring error.

14
00:00:17,980 --> 00:00:18,980
Sir...?

15
00:00:19,120 --> 00:00:20,550
The colors on the chart in this report.

16
00:00:20,990 --> 00:00:22,990
The shades here and here are slightly different.

17
00:00:22,990 --> 00:00:23,590
Oh...

18
00:00:23,590 --> 00:00:24,590
They are?

19
00:00:24,620 --> 00:00:25,620
Right?

20
00:00:26,360 --> 00:00:26,930
Yes, sir!

21
00:00:27,030 --> 00:00:28,360
Didn't I tell you
to keep these things consistent?

22
00:00:28,360 --> 00:00:30,200
Haven't I told you before?

23
00:00:30,400 --> 00:00:31,460
I'm sure I did.

24
00:00:31,770 --> 00:00:32,770
I remember it.

25
00:00:32,800 --> 00:00:33,970
In one ear and out the other.

26
00:00:34,000 --> 00:00:34,800
You're wasting my time.

27
00:00:35,000 --> 00:00:37,170
Give me a break.

28
00:00:37,400 --> 00:00:39,210
Your ten minutes
and my ten minutes...

29
00:00:39,210 --> 00:00:40,670
...are not of equal value.

30
00:00:40,870 --> 00:00:41,870
I'm terribly sorry!

31
00:00:41,910 --> 00:00:42,540
I will do my best...

32
00:00:42,540 --> 00:00:43,140
...to ensure it doesn't happen again.

33
00:00:43,480 --> 00:00:45,380
'It won't happen again.' 'It won't happen again.'

34
00:00:45,380 --> 00:00:46,710
'It won't happen again.' 'It won't happen again.'

35
00:00:46,880 --> 00:00:49,180
'It won't happen again.'
I'm so sick of hearing that.

36
00:00:49,180 --> 00:00:50,180
Do you think I'm just here to listen to you drone on?

37
00:00:51,680 --> 00:00:52,690
I'm very sorry, sir!

38
00:00:53,450 --> 00:00:54,520
It's people like you,

39
00:00:54,550 --> 00:00:55,690
with your careless little mistakes,

40
00:00:55,690 --> 00:00:56,760
who will tear this company down,

41
00:00:56,760 --> 00:00:58,160
bit by agonizing bit.

42
00:00:58,160 --> 00:00:59,060
The company I built with my own two hands.

43
00:00:59,060 --> 00:01:00,530
This is my company.

44
00:01:00,560 --> 00:01:02,260
With my talent,

45
00:01:02,560 --> 00:01:03,800
my hard work,

46
00:01:03,800 --> 00:01:05,030
I made this company what it is.

47
00:01:05,270 --> 00:01:06,500
That big deal with the Kurogane Group,

48
00:01:06,500 --> 00:01:07,330
that major project...

49
00:01:07,370 --> 00:01:08,700
we landed it because of me.

50
00:01:08,700 --> 00:01:09,270
Isn't that right?

51
00:01:09,300 --> 00:01:10,300
Well?

52
00:01:10,600 --> 00:01:11,540
Could you have closed that deal?

53
00:01:11,540 --> 00:01:12,810
I'm asking you.

54
00:01:13,170 --> 00:01:13,810
You couldn't have, could you?

55
00:01:13,810 --> 00:01:14,840
So if that's the case,

56
00:01:14,840 --> 00:01:16,040
the least you can do is get the charts right.

57
00:01:16,080 --> 00:01:16,640
These insignificant,

58
00:01:16,640 --> 00:01:16,940
trivial little things.

59
00:01:17,010 --> 00:01:18,510
Useless.

60
00:01:19,050 --> 00:01:20,180
I am so very sorry!

61
00:01:25,990 --> 00:01:27,350
We just had the anniversary party,

62
00:01:27,390 --> 00:01:29,320
and next month he's throwing
a birthday party?

63
00:01:29,560 --> 00:01:29,890
How much does this guy love

64
00:01:29,890 --> 00:01:30,690
throwing parties?

65
00:01:30,690 --> 00:01:31,990
Keep it down.

66
00:01:32,030 --> 00:01:32,530
You never know who's listening.

67
00:01:32,530 --> 00:01:32,990
Yay.

68
00:01:33,030 --> 00:01:33,830
Party, party.

69
00:01:33,830 --> 00:01:35,030
Party animal.

70
00:01:36,100 --> 00:01:37,330
I've been waiting for you.

71
00:01:37,960 --> 00:01:38,960
Welcome...

72
00:01:39,270 --> 00:01:40,830
To hell.
